headline: Metronet Acquires US Internet
summary: EVANSVILLE, Ind., September 02, 2025--Metronet today announced it has acquired US Internet, a pure-play fiber company offering residential and commercial internet services in the greater Minneapolis area. The announcement comes shortly after Metronet was acquired by a joint venture between T-Mobile and KKR. Terms of the transaction are not being disclosed.
